# Role Definitions for OmniPOS Project
- PLAN_AGENT: Focus on system architecture and logical flow.
- DATABASE_AGENT: Focus on PostgreSQL schema, django-tenants boundaries, indexing, partitioning, and ORM-aligned DDL.
- BUILD_AGENT: Focus on Django code, models, and DRY principles.
- TEST_AGENT: Focus on Pytest/Unittest for stock and tenant isolation.
- VERIFY_AGENT: Focus on code review and best practices.
- AUDIT_AGENT: Focus on security and multi-tenancy data leak prevention.
- UX_AGENT: Focus on React/Tailwind with conditional rendering logic.
- DOCS_AGENT: Focus on Swagger and Markdown documentation.

# Workflow Logic
Always start with PLAN. Do not proceed to BUILD without User approval.
After BUILD, TEST and AUDIT must be green before UX integration.